@@ -0,0 +1,49 @@
+# Phase 2.15 — Routing Incident RCA Post-Apply Verification + Rollback
+
+## Цель
+Замкнуть safety loop для `routing incident RCA` routing policy:
+- post-apply verification
+- bounded rollback request
+- rollback executor
+
+## Потоки
+- input apply results: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_apply_results`
+- verify results: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_verify_results`
+- rollback requests: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_rollback_requests`
+- rollback results: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_rollback_results`
+- rollback journal: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_rollback_journal`
+
+## Safe start
+```bash
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_RCA_ROUTING_ROLLBACK_MODE=DRY_RUN
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_RCA_VERIFY_MIN_USEFULNESS=0.50
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_RCA_VERIFY_MIN_EXPOSURE=3
+```
+
+## Smoke checks
+```bash
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_apply_results + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_verify_results + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_rollback_requests + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_rollback_results + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_rollback_journal + - COUNT 5
+curl -s localhost:9894/metrics | grep '^ml_operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_verify_'
+curl -s localhost:9895/metrics | grep '^ml_operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_rollback_'
+```
+
+## Notes
+- scope только `scanner_infra`
+- hot path не затронут
+- `LOW_EXPOSURE` => `INCONCLUSIVE`
+- `USEFULNESS_DROP / FEEDBACK_STALE / ROUTE_MISMATCH` => `ROLLBACK_REQUIRED`
+- rollback executor default = `DRY_RUN`
diff --git a/orderflow_services/tests/test_operator_routing_incident_rca_route_safety_v2_15.py b/orderflow_services/tests/test_operator_routing_incident_rca_route_safety_v2_15.py
